#

Tuna Poke Bowl

15 min
$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

SeafoodSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Cuisine:

Hawaiian

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickHealthyFresh

Description

A refreshing bowl of marinated tuna, fresh vegetables, and a hint of umami flavor, perfect for a quick meal.

Ingredients

  • sushi-grade tuna: 1 cup, diced
  • cooked white rice or brown rice: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1/2, sliced
  • carrot: 1, shredded
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • green onions: 2, chopped
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • sesame oil: 1 teaspoon
  • rice vinegar: 1 teaspoon
  • sesame seeds: 1 teaspoon
